[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0433","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0433.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0248","title":"SSH sshd 认证代理竞争条件漏洞","description":"SSH 服务软件 sshd 1.2.17 版本的身份认证代理机制存在竞争条件漏洞（Race Condition）。远程攻击者在认证窗口内利用时序差向目标发送精心构造的认证请求，可在合法用户完成认证前截获或替换其身份凭证，从而窃取其他用户的 SSH 登录凭据并获得未授权访问。该漏洞影响早期 SSH 协议实现，利用难度较低，可导致敏感信息泄露和系统被控。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0248"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.860","remediation":"升级至 sshd 1.2.18 及以上版本，该版本已修复认证代理机制中的条件竞争漏洞。也可迁移至 OpenSSH（自 1999 年起开源维护），并保持版本更新。若无法升级，限制对 ssh-agent 的本地访问权限，仅允许受信任用户使用代理转发功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://oliver.efri.hr/~crv/security/bugs/mUNIXes/ssh2.html","http://www.uni-karlsruhe.de/~ig25/ssh-faq/ssh-faq-6.html#ss6.1","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0248.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0248.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0248","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0248.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0248.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0248.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vhcr-j22h-735c/GHSA-vhcr-j22h-735c.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82092/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0248.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0433.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0428","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0428.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0243","title":"Linux cfingerd 远程权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux cfingerd（可配置的 Finger 服务守护进程）存在远程权限提升漏洞，未经身份认证的攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的 Finger 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获取目标系统 root 最高权限，完全控制受影响服务器。该漏洞影响多个 Linux 发行版中运行的 cfingerd 服务，攻击者无需任何认证即可远程发起攻击，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0243"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.250","remediation":"立即停止并卸载 cfingerd 服务（`systemctl stop cfingerd && apt-get remove cfingerd` 或 `yum remove cfingerd`）。cfingerd 已在 2000 年代初停止维护，不存在补丁修复。建议在 iptables 或防火墙中封禁 TCP 端口 79，同时禁用 finger 协议。改用现代认证机制（如 LDAP/SSSD）替代 finger 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.geocrawler.com/archives/3/92/1996/9/0/2217716/","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0243","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0243.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q27j-g75f-h573/GHSA-q27j-g75f-h573.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/cfinger_format_bug.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80889/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0243.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0428.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0425","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0425.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0240","title":"防火墙或过滤器 IP分片SYN数据包 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"部分防火墙或网络过滤器在处理分片 SYN 数据包时存在策略绕过漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标网络发送设置了 IP 保留位的特制分片 SYN 数据包，绕过防火墙或过滤器的访问控制规则，未经授权访问受保护的内部网络资源。该漏洞影响多种品牌和型号的防火墙产品，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商通过更新防火墙的分片重组和标志位检查逻辑修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0240"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.897","remediation":"对防火墙启用状态检测（Stateful Inspection）功能，确保所有IP分片报文在重组完成后再进行规则匹配，禁止直接放行分片SYN包。同时在防火墙上配置策略丢弃IP头部保留位非零的数据包，并禁用非必要接口的IP路由转发功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0240","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0240","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0240.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9w2q-p353-cvp5/GHSA-9w2q-p353-cvp5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0425.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0416","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0416.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0231","title":"IP-Switch IMail 和 Seattle Labs Slmail 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IP-Switch IMail 与 Seattle Labs Slmail 2.6 邮件服务软件中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 SMTP 服务发送超长 VRFY 命令参数触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致服务拒绝服务，在特定条件下可进一步实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响上述邮件系统的 SMTP 组件，利用无需认证，攻击门槛较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0231"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.770","remediation":"该漏洞存在于 SLMail 2.6 及更早版本的 VRFY 命令处理中，超长参数导致栈缓冲区溢出。厂商后续版本已修复此问题，建议尽快升级至 SLMail 3.0 及以上版本，或迁移至 Ipswitch IMail 最新版本。若无法立即升级，应在 SMTP 代理或 IPS 设备上限制 VRFY 命令参数长度不超过 256 字节，并禁用 VRFY/EXPN 命令以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0231","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0231","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0231.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5r6m-8793-wrhh/GHSA-5r6m-8793-wrhh.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/slmail.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80916/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0416.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0410","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0410.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0220","title":"IRC Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IRC 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标 IRC 服务器发送特制数据包，导致服务器进程崩溃，使其无法为正常用户提供聊天服务。该漏洞影响多种 IRC 服务器软件，攻击者仅需具备网络访问能力即可触发，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0220"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.423","remediation":"升级 ircd 至 2.10.3 及以上版本，该版本已修复因畸形数据包导致的服务器崩溃问题。对于无法升级的旧系统，可在 IRC 服务前端部署 TCP 代理或应用层防火墙，过滤异常连接请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0220","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0220.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0220","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9rhw-5hch-3fh6/GHSA-9rhw-5hch-3fh6.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0220.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80885/info.html","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0220.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0410.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0390","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0390.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0205","title":"Eric Allman Sendmail 8.6.11/8.6.12 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.6.11 及 8.6.12 版本存在拒绝服务漏洞。作为广泛使用的邮件传输代理（MTA），Sendmail 在处理特制的网络请求时存在缺陷，未经认证的远程攻击者可利用此漏洞向目标服务器发送恶意构造的数据包，导致 Sendmail 服务进程崩溃或停止响应，从而造成邮件服务中断。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需任何身份认证即可远程触发，影响系统可用性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0205"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:54.477","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.6.13 或更高版本，该版本已修复此拒绝服务漏洞。若无法立即升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中限制连接速率和最大并发连接数，并在网络边界启用流量过滤以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0205"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0390.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0383","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0383.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0200","title":"Microsoft Windows NT FTP Server 未授权访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT FTP 服务器（WFTP）在默认配置中启用了无密码的 guest 账户，远程攻击者可利用任意用户名和密码成功登录 FTP 服务器，获取未经授权的文件访问权限。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统，攻击者无需任何身份认证即可利用，对系统的机密性构成严重威胁。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0200"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.867","remediation":"立即禁用 Windows NT 的 Guest 帐户（或为其设置强密码），并配置 FTP 服务禁止匿名/来宾登录。在 FTP 服务器上设置用户权限最小化，限制可访问目录。建议升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 2016/2019/2022），因 Windows NT 已停止安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.microsoft.com/technet/support/kb.asp?ID=137853"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0383.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0382","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0382.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0198","title":"多个Unix系统 finger服务 远程信息泄露漏洞","description":"Finger 服务（TCP 79 端口）存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标发送 finger 查询请求（如 finger .@host），获取系统上的用户账户列表及登录状态。该漏洞源于 Finger 协议默认未对查询请求做访问控制，导致攻击者可借此收集有效用户名，为进一步的暴力破解或社会工程学攻击提供基础。影响运行 Finger 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 10.0。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0198"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.610","remediation":"立即禁用 finger 服务：在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释或删除 finger 行并重启服务（`kill -HUP <inetd_pid>`），或执行 `systemctl disable finger`（现代系统）。同时使用防火墙阻断外部对 tcp/79 端口的访问。如确需使用，改用 cfingerd 并限制输出信息量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/8378"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0382.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0380","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0380.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0197","title":"多种Unix操作系统 Finger 远程信息泄露漏洞","description":"Finger 服务（TCP 79 端口）存在用户信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需任何认证，通过发送 `finger 0@host` 查询即可获取目标系统上的用户账户信息，包括用户名、真实姓名、终端状态、最后登录时间等敏感数据。攻击者可利用这些信息进行账户枚举，为后续的暴力破解或社会工程学攻击奠定基础。该漏洞影响运行 Finger 服务的各类 Unix/Linux 系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0197"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.497","remediation":"立即在系统层面禁用 finger 服务：Systemd 系统执行 `systemctl stop finger && systemctl disable finger`，SysVinit 系统执行 `service finger stop && chkconfig finger off`。同时在防火墙（iptables/nftables）阻止入站连接端口 79/tcp。如确需远程查询功能，替换为受限版本如 `finge-rus` 并限制查询来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/8378"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0380.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0370","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0370.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0187","title":"Microsoft IIS 远程任意命令执行漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0187 已被废弃，它是 CVE-1999-0022 的重复编号。CVE-1999-0022 描述的是 rdist（远程文件分发工具）中 expstr() 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户可利用该漏洞通过精心构造的数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SunOS/Solaris、SGI IRIX、HP-UX、IBM AIX、FreeBSD 等多个 Unix 系统，攻击者只需拥有本地账户即可实施提权攻击，危害等级高危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0187"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:55.743","remediation":"请立即安装对应 Unix 厂商（如 Sun 安全公告 #00179、SGI IRIX 6.4/6.5 补丁）提供的 rdist 补丁，或升级操作系统至修复版本。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/rdist` 移除 rdist 的 setuid 位，或直接删除 rdist 并在需要时改用 rsync/scp 等替代工具。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0370.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0251","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0251.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0110","title":"Sun Solaris fdformat 命令缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0110 已被 CVE 组织废弃，该编号是 CVE-1999-0315 的重复项，因原始描述中的拼写错误导致未能及时识别为重复记录。实际对应漏洞为：Sun Solaris 系统中 fdformat 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该命令传递特制输入参数触发溢出，覆盖内存数据并执行任意代码，从而获取 root 权限。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限方可利用，影响 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1/7.0 等版本，CVSS v2 评分为 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0110"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:55.093","remediation":"安装 Sun 安全公告 #138 提供的对应 Solaris 版本补丁：Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1/7.0 分别有对应补丁包。如系统已停止官方支持，建议升级至 Solaris 10 或更新版本。临时缓解措施：限制不可信本地用户登录系统，移除 fdformat 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/fdformat）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0251.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0067","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0067.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0020","title":"多种厂商 TCP/IP 实现 Land 攻击拒绝服务漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0020 已被标识为无效编号（REJECT），其内容与 CVE-1999-0032 重复。对应漏洞为 BSD 系列系统（含 Linux）中 lpr 打印服务的缓冲区溢出漏洞：lpr 在处理 -C（classification）命令行选项时未对用户输入长度进行充分校验，本地攻击者可传入超长参数触发栈缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。影响范围涵盖多款 BSD 衍生操作系统及 Linux 发行版，攻击前提是拥有目标系统的本地 shell 访问权限，属于本地提权漏洞，CVSS v2.0 评分为 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0020"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:53.530","remediation":"此 CVE 为重复项，实际漏洞为 CVE-1999-0032（Land 攻击：源目 IP/端口相同的 TCP SYN 包导致系统崩溃）。修复措施：升级操作系统至已修复该漏洞的版本（如 Windows NT 4.0 SP4 以上、Linux 2.0.34 以上、Solaris 2.6 及以上补丁）；在边界防火墙上配置规则丢弃源地址等于目标地址的入站 IP 包；路由器上启用 uRPF（单播反向路径转发）过滤。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0067.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0991","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0991.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0665","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表键值配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中存在一个应用程序关键注册表项值配置不当的安全漏洞，该注册表项被设置为不安全的值，导致系统安全策略被绕过。远程攻击者可利用此漏洞结合其他攻击手段实现对目标系统的完全控制，包括执行任意代码、安装程序、查看更改或删除数据，以及创建拥有完全权限的新账户。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0665"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对 Windows NT 4.0 的安全更新，修正注册表键值为安全配置。如无法安装补丁，手动检查并修正 `HKLM` 下相关键值权限为只读，限制非授权修改。该系统已停止支持，建议升级至受支持 Windows 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0665","https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0665"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0991.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0979","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0979.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0657","title":"Deerfield WinGate 开放代理配置不当漏洞","description":"WinGate 是一款 Windows 平台常用的代理服务器软件，默认配置下其 SOCKS（TCP 1080）、HTTP（TCP 80）及 Telnet（TCP 23）等代理服务可能监听在 0.0.0.0 即所有网络接口上，导致公网任意主机均可连接并使用该代理服务转发流量。远程攻击者可将暴露的 WinGate 服务器用作开放代理中继，从而隐藏攻击来源、转发垃圾邮件或扫描内网资源。此条目属于安全配置不当问题而非软件代码缺陷，影响 WinGate 全版本默认部署场景。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0657"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"在 WinGate GateKeeper 管理控制台中设置绑定策略，将 HTTP/SOCKS/Telnet 代理服务的监听地址限制为内网 IP，禁止绑定 0.0.0.0；同时配置客户端访问规则，只允许授权 IP 段使用代理服务。如无法通过配置限制，建议在边界防火墙上阻断外部对 TCP 1080/80/23 等端口的入站访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0657","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0657"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0979.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0962","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0962.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0644","title":"通用 NNTP 新闻组服务配置不当漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0644 是一个已被驳回（REJECT）的候选编号，原条目仅描述「NNTP 新闻服务正在运行」这一服务配置状态，而非软件安全缺陷。NNTP（网络新闻传输协议）作为面向互联网的系统服务时，默认不要求用户认证且通信未加密传输，攻击者可能通过中间人攻击截获或篡改传输内容。该配置本身不直接引入安全漏洞，但可能增加系统攻击面，建议在不需要时禁用 NNTP 服务，或通过 SSL/TLS 隧道封装以保护通信安全。此类配置问题更适合通过通用配置枚举（CCE）来规范管理。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0644"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2023-11-06","remediation":"若业务不需要 NNTP 新闻服务，建议在服务器上停止并禁用 NNTP 服务（Linux 关闭 innd 或 nntpd 服务，Windows 关闭 Microsoft NNTP Service 或禁用相应端口 119/TCP）。若确需使用，应配置身份认证、限制可访问源 IP，并确保仅在内网可访问。同时建议将 NNTP 服务置于防火墙后，不在公网暴露 119/TCP 端口。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0644"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0962.toml"}]